      <title>丹格特因涉嫌垄断放弃钢铁投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dangote-to-scrap-steel-investment-over-allegations-of-monopoly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲首富阿里科·丹格特取消了在尼日利亚投资新钢铁厂的计划，此前尼日利亚政府指责他试图利用在西非国家新建的炼油厂垄断市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dangote-to-scrap-steel-investment-over-allegations-of-monopoly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 07:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝利的沉默引发英国央行 8 月降息悬念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利（Andrew Bailey）已经沉默了两个月，这让每个人都无法猜测利率将何时发生重大变化，也没有太多可参考的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
