      <title>美国通胀率下降将有助于安抚美联储</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/fed-rate-cuts-latest-downshifting-us-inflation-will-help-reassure-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着新的迹象显示通胀正在减弱且经济活动正在放缓，未来一周美联储降息的走向将更加清晰。]]></description>
